org.opentosca.toscana.plugins.cloudformation.visitor

Class CloudFormationVisitor

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.opentosca.toscana.plugins.cloudformation.visitor.CloudFormationVisitor
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    CheckModelNodeVisitor, CheckModelRelationshipVisitor, PrepareModelNodeVisitor, PrepareModelRelationshipVisitor, TransformModelNodeVisitor

    public abstract class CloudFormationVisitor
extends java.lang.Object
    Abstract class that is the base to all visitors (NodeVisitor, StrictNodeVisitor, RelationshipVisitor), StrictRelationshipVisitor for the CloudFormation plugin.
    It provides general function, a logger, the topology of the EffectiveModel and the CloudFormationModule.
